The paper deals with machine learning algorithms and game theory, which are both core topics in computer science. The focus on prediction algorithms and their strategic use suggests that cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The use of game theory also suggests cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) as a likely sub-category. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures (cs.DS), and information theory (cs.IT) in its analysis and modeling.
